Vectorized weights_seasonal_decay()

Source: R/weights_seasonal.R
weights_seasonal_decay_vec.Rd

Vectorized weights_seasonal_decay()

Usage

weights_seasonal_decay_vec(alphas_seasonal_decay, n, period_length)

Examples

t(vapply(
  X = c(1, 0.2, 0.5, 0.8, 0),
  FUN = weights_seasonal_decay,
  n = 50,
  period_length = 12,
  FUN.VALUE = numeric(50),
  USE.NAMES = FALSE
))
